@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### =========================
### 0. 회원가입 - 사용자 A (클라이언트 예정)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client1@test.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "name": "Client One",
  "nickname": "client1"
}

### =========================
### 1. 회원가입 - 사용자 B (프리랜서 예정)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "freelancer1@test.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "name": "Freelancer One",
  "nickname": "freelancer1"
}

### =========================
### 2. 로그인 - 사용자 A
### 응답의 accessToken 복사해서 clientToken에 넣기
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client1@test.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

###
@clientToken =eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbGllbnQxQHRlc3QuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjoxLCJyb2xlIjoiQ0xJRU5UIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2MjQwOTk0LCJleHAiOjE3NzYyNDQ1OTR9.nJq7dSLy9rlwCdpyTJ01vWVBkZk_aUKEklAQpQThLsHrwzKCh8IOFOPI6JFd_t2P

### =========================
### 3. 로그인 - 사용자 B
### 응답의 accessToken 복사해서 freelancerToken에 넣기
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "freelancer1@test.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

###
@freelancerToken = eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJmcmVlbGFuY2VyMUB0ZXN0LmNvbSIsInVzZXJJZCI6Miwicm9sZSI6IkZSRUVMQU5DRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzYyMzgyNTcsImV4cCI6MTc3NjI0MTg1N30.Uk0Fbl9mA-Vo7wDKraKOPmXRN8I-VCzSyaNIapwdd1ZpBFc4551wIaSgc9Z6ICkE

### =========================
### 4. 사용자 A 온보딩 (CLIENT 권한)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/onboarding
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "nickname": "client1",
  "role": "CLIENT",
  "clientProfile": {
    "companyName": "DevNear Client Co",
    "bn": "123-45-67890",
    "representativeName": "홍길동",
    "introduction": "채팅 테스트용 클라이언트",
    "homepageUrl": "https://example.com",
    "phoneNum": "010-1234-5678"
  }
}

### 온보딩 후 새 토큰이 오면 아래에 다시 붙여넣기
@clientRoleToken = eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbGllbnQxQHRlc3QuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjoxLCJyb2xlIjoiQ0xJRU5UIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2MjM2Mzc0LCJleHAiOjE3NzYzMjI3NzR9.8DSi7Zg_mdt586yg3LeYsb-JOmebFwRzNf4NkO2EWlURuUE46JE8khdBS48RBPbUbN9aaTzqpa7AwkKmUsb15g

### =========================
### 5. 사용자 B 온보딩 전 기본 스킬 조회
### 스킬 ID 확인용
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/skills/default

### =========================
### 6. 사용자 B 온보딩 (FREELANCER 권한)
### skillIds는 위 조회 결과의 실제 ID로 수정
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/onboarding
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}

{
  "nickname": "freelancer1",
  "role": "FREELANCER",
  "freelancerProfile": {
    "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/profile.png",
    "introduction": "채팅 테스트용 프리랜서",
    "location": "서울 강남구",
    "latitude": 37.4979,
    "longitude": 127.0276,
    "hourlyRate": 30000,
    "workStyle": "HYBRID",
    "isActive": true,
    "skillIds": [1]
  }
}

### 온보딩 후 새 토큰이 오면 아래에 다시 붙여넣기
@freelancerRoleToken = eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJmcmVlbGFuY2VyMUB0ZXN0LmNvbSIsInVzZXJJZCI6Miwicm9sZSI6IkZSRUVMQU5DRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzYyMzc1NDMsImV4cCI6MTc3NjMyMzk0M30.piiU3GwzkiW4vBJbfW9TSbngYRgj13F-t3Hf30V2c_kvVhNekm93ql7e8RYFaxBG6zGrtuPw6p9pDOB9rUgPuw

### =========================
### 7. 사용자 A 내 정보 조회
### userId 확인용
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{clientRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 8. 사용자 B 내 정보 조회
### userId 확인용
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 9. 프로젝트 생성 - 사용자 A
### 응답의 projectId 확인
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientRoleToken}}

{
  "projectName": "채팅 테스트 프로젝트",
  "budget": 100000,
  "deadline": "2026-12-31",
  "detail": "1:1 채팅 테스트용 프로젝트",
  "online": true,
  "offline": false,
  "skillIds": [1]
}

### =========================
### 10. 채팅방 생성
### projectId, targetUserId는 실제 값으로 수정
### targetUserId는 사용자 B의 users.user_id 값
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientRoleToken}}

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "targetUserId": 2
}

### =========================
### 11. 내 채팅방 목록 조회 - 사용자 A
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{clientRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 12. 내 채팅방 목록 조회 - 사용자 B
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 13. 특정 채팅방 메시지 조회
### roomId는 실제 생성된 값으로 수정
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/rooms/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{clientRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 14. 읽음 처리
### =========================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/rooms/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerRoleToken}}

### =========================
### 15. WebSocket/STOMP 수동 테스트 정보
### endpoint: ws://localhost:8080/ws-chat
### connect header: Authorization: Bearer {clientRoleToken}
### subscribe: /sub/chat/rooms/1
### publish: /pub/chat/send
### body:
### {"roomId":1,"content":"안녕하세요"}
### =========================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbGllbnQxQHRlc3QuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjoxLCJyb2xlIjoiQ0xJRU5UIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2MjQwOTk0LCJleHAiOjE3NzYyNDQ1OTR9.nJq7dSLy9rlwCdpyTJ01vWVBkZk_aUKEklAQpQThLsHrwzKCh8IOFOPI6JFd_t2P
